Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学童子军  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Science Scouts, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次的义卖严肃得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here business is serious as a rattlesnake bite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以可不能搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let's make sure we don't mess it up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是赚得够多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we earn enough money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后就能有钱去火星旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can finally afford that trip to Mars
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出发卖饼干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get out there and sell these biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  科学队长珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Science Master Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵什么吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all that racket?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, ma'ams
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.40,0:01:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想来买点科学童子军饼干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy some Science Scouts biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Science?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种玩意就是一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That malarkey ain't real
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那个年代有炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back in my day, we had alchemy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对我们来说早就够用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that was good enough for us
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玛丽  今天都星期三了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mary, it's Wednesday
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来削掉我脚上的肿块
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to shave down my bunions
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是屋主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you the man of the house?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人在休眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master is in repose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你的主人应该会愿意醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, perhaps your master would like to wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝新鲜现烤的饼干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to some fresh-baked biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.99,0:02:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可不喜欢固体食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't care for solid foods
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过主人会口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master does get thirsty though
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1098,290)}拉里健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小姐兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sup, little lady bro?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有考虑过买点科学童子军饼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you considered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,purchasing some Science Scout bis--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  能量棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, energy bars?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮你强身健体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They will fill you with the fuel for fitness
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.19,0:02:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里我确实得补补碳水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Larry does need to carbo load
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买十二盒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a dozen boxes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖出第一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got our first sale
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我关节好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My aching knuckles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一定敲了一百万扇门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have knocked on a million doors today
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹蟹的美味小点心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tasty morsels for the Krabsy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Claws off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这钱可是科学童子军的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That money belongs to the Science Scouts
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是我卖饼干赚来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it from selling biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖饼干是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Selling biscuitses, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天的饼干义卖赚得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that was some
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fancy biscuit hawking yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但今天  我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but today, we're going to--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那边陪着蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's over there with Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟那条愁眉苦脸的章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that sad-looking octopus
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.40,0:04:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是在为裤头村顶级饼干义卖队效命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's working with the premier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,biscuit-selling team in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's what he's doing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还得卖蟹堡涂鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've got some Krusty Doodles to sell
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Doodles?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是不新鲜的蟹黄堡面包而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are just stale Krabby Patty buns
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.42,0:04:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美陈酿  撒有肉桂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aged to perfection and sprinkled with cinnamon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, scram
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是蟹堡童子军的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Krusty Scout territory
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美  这里可是科学童子军的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, this is Science Scout territory
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不来打个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little wager?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.39,0:04:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁今天饼干卖得最多  谁就能继续卖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever sells the most biscuits today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gets to keep selling
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,输的那队以后永远不准再卖饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the loser leaves the biscuit biz forever
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deal
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个来推销的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A solicitor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友  想不想来买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend, how would you like to buy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全海洋最有收藏价值的点心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the most collectible snack in the whole ocean?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是全新未拆封的薄荷饼干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're mint biscuits in mint condition
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说全新未拆封吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mint, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想尝到饼干真正的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want real biscuit flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来尝尝看蟹堡涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,try a Krusty Doodle instead
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的角色扮演太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your cosplay is terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll pass
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来三盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me three boxes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想卖饼干得再可爱点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to move biscuits, you gotta be cuter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll help you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你可爱不少了  看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're adorable, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,视网膜脱落了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My retinas detached
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍啊  你好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pearl, don't you look cute?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在卖饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm selling biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的童子军队筹钱上火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so my scout troop can go to Mars
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找找钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get my purse
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来买我的饼干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy my biscuits instead
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你眼睛怎么了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your eyes, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're blowing it again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你正确示范
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  我可爱的阿芙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, my sweet Puffikins
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不来我这买点饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't you buy some biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我这只螃蟹偷走了你的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the only crab to ever steal your heart?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that does sound nice
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的饼干才更好  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My biscuits are better, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听她的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己找人家义卖去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find your own house to sell at
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来我这买饼干才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your biscuit right here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买我的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buy mine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想来买点饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy some biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定不想买饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to buy some biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的超辣肉桂饼干买不买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about our super spicy cinnamon biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么大家都不叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did everyone stop yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,610)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这次的饼干生意我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like the biscuit business is all mine now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能让他赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We ain't letting him win this one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  科学童子军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Science Scouts
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是罢休吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not let it go, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正镇上就只剩一个地方能卖饼干了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one place left in town to sell to anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,养老院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the old folks home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.06,0:07:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得把饼干卖给所有老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'd have to sell to every single oldie there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能打败我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to beat me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来全靠你了  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's up to you, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.37,0:07:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was my plan
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西应该是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe this belongs to you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My biscuits
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,376)}荫凉滩\N疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞破坏最爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats sabotage-y
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me brakes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've been sabotagied
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,526)}优惠炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,492)}床垫厂
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想要饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你呢  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about you, mister?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想来找我这可爱小女孩买饼干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy some biscuits from a sweet little girl?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙的假牙都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's chompers have gone missing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.22,0:09:01.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没牙还怎么咀嚼饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to chew biscuits
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if we ain't got no teeth?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像把大家的假牙都借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I borrowed everyone's dentures
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来买软软糯糯的饼干糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your biscuit mush right here, nice and soft
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经咀嚼过了  可以不用再嚼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We do the chewing so you don't have to
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手工饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Homemade biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好美味的糊糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lovely mush
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to call it a day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活到老学到老  小珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Live and learn, Pearly girl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们卖饼干注定要玩完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just the way the biscuit bounces
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的饼干再咀嚼糊一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make mine extra mushy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Pearly girl
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很遗憾你这次比拼没赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry you didn't win the competition
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't lose yet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我想起来还能再找一个人卖饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, I realized there was one more person to sell to
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我正好知道怎么说服他买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I know how to get him to buy anything
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like where this is going
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买我的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy my biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I can't--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.11,0:10:38.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:38.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  我这就买你的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll buy your biscuits
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去火星了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to Mars
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,穿越太空之后
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前的饼干义卖赚得真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was some mighty fine selling
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学童子军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Science Scouts
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于有钱可以大胆扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, we can afford to boldly expand
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挺进新的饼干市场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into new biscuit markets
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  地球生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Earth creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要买点太空饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to purchase some Astro Biscuits?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在攒钱去地球旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are raising money for a trip to Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是赚得够多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we earn enough money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后就能有钱去木星了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can afford a trip to Jupiter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.18,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs160\fsp40\c&H00FFB5&}驾校幸存学员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,670)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:52.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(626,454)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(772,654)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:50.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(748,498)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船整整一里都卡在倒挡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My boat was stuck in reverse for a whole mile
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向左转  开上了一座超大弹簧山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I turned left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and backed into a mountain of giant springs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太强了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Righteous, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后船往前弹了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, the boat sprung forward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开上了还没完工的大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,up onto an unfinished bridge
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那里弹弹跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we bounced--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿梭在桥墩之间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from column to column
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后被一个起重机钩住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and got caught on the hook of a construction crane
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挂在上面荡过整座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we swung out over the city
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后着陆到了个垃圾箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we landed on a garbage dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.10,0:12:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你夸张地复述上一节驾驶课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for that melodramatic retelling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of our last driving lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙突然就冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wall came out of nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Settle down, class
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很高兴能宣布今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm elated to announce that today
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.66,0:12:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又多了一个新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have a new driving student with us
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in and introduce yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你能给我这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for this opportunity
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加速绿灯是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Acceleration T. Greenlight's the name
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教会学员驾驶就是我的拿手好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and teaching driving is my game
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.14,0:13:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是绿灯驾校的所有者及经营者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner and operator
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Greenlight Driving School
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, mister, you can just--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能保证大家都能领到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I guarantee a driver's license to anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕着教学楼开一圈  包开包会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after only one drive around the block
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且学费只要泡芙老师的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and at half the price that Mrs. Puff charges
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前对付过他这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've dealt with his kind before
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  不能再回去坐牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am not going back to the slammer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕教学楼开一圈  包你领驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once around the block and your license is a lock
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们  你们要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class, where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,170)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎  白痴们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, suckers--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  学员们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, students--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1046,534)}绿灯驾校
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来就读绿灯驾校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Greenlight Driving School
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.61,0:14:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人居然全都抛下我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe everyone left me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并不是所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might have known
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:17.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1286,690)}墙
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.17,0:14:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.84,0:14:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刹车  刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brakes, brakes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是今天的学费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's for today's lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别一下子都花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't spend it all in one place
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you next week
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  绕着教学楼开一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes siree, once around the block
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1564,686)}裤头村驾照\N史酷特\N裤头村\N酷乐湖{\fnArial}1434{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功领到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a licensed driver
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gnarly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a license
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个加速绿灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Acceleration T. Greenlight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,账单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bills?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逾期  欠债
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Overdue, delinquent?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不还清就去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Pay or die?"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.35,0:15:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一周就教一次海绵宝宝还怎么还债啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How will I ever pay these bills
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,teaching SpongeBob only once a week?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上船学下一课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop in for your next lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你搞错了吧  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天不上课的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's not my lesson day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚把你升级成超级黄金学员了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just upgraded you to Super Gold status
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后你每天都得来上课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have lessons every day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然相应的费用该付还得付
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the corresponding fees, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  可我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快开船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, drive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't look
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,380)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looky there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那家开得特成功的驾校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that really successful driving school
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can drive now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  输家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, loser
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对你忠诚  而且只对你忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm loyal to you and only you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天上的驾驶课可真漫长啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a long day's driving lesson, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来上下一节课了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, time for your next lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好是好  可现在都大半夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's the middle of the night
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的课程是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight's lesson is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半夜行船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Late-night driving
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然还得再额外上交课程费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, there'll be an extra fee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.69,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半夜行船的重中之重就是保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most important part
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of night driving is staying awake
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放点大声的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some loud music
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来点咖啡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And coffee should do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挡道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the road
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:46.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,292)}危险  雾堤
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天早上上课再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in the morning for tomorrow's lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可明天星期天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow is Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你星期天也得来上驾驶课  小傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your Sunday driver lesson, you silly billy boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我是小傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm a silly billy boy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,348)}溜冰场
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天总算能自己做主了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, a day to myself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天的课程是冰上行船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's lesson, ice driving
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朝打滑方向打方向盘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn into the slide
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松开油门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Foot off the gas
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向海神王祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pray to Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真的有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That actually worked
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.97,0:18:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好就需要独处的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just what I needed, some me time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要上什么课了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What lesson now?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山路行船课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mountain driving lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面的小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out below
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1678,866)}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,534)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护士  我现在要拉开他的拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse, I'm unzipping him now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  你在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, are you in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会塞得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would I fit in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  里面的空间只能装得下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's only room for one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.06,0:19:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来上你下一节驾驶课了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for your next driving lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是泡芙老师  我完全破产了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mrs. Puff, I'm totally broke
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也没钱交学费了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't pay for any more lessons
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.82,0:19:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's the end of the road for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱能吃点午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we get some lunch now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肚子空荡荡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your stomach is empty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of business
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:20:00.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114,586)}停业
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为我的驾校能开一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought my school would last forever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光他自己一个海绵就是拆迁队了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the one-sponge wrecking crew
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我居然一直都做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I've been going about this all wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342,442)}裤头村驾照\N小蜗\N裤头村\N贝壳街{\fnArial}124{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上路愉快  蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy trails, snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是泡芙老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么风把你吹来我这所小驾校的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What brings you to my humble driving school?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说你随随便便就能让学员领到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You say you can get any student a license
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要上一节课就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with just one lesson?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guaranteed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边要给你个冤大头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got a live one for you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你多半用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领到驾照的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The trick to being a licensed driver
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在于绕着教学楼开一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is going once around the block
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没学  放我出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't learned "let me out" yet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过可以给你见识一下我学到的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'll show you what I have learned
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停下这艘船  我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop this boat, I beg of you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.47,0:21:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当好乘客的秘诀就是放弃一切控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The trick to being a passenger is to give up all control
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,252)}警察局
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's my driving?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.99,0:21:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你逮到了恶名昭彰的加速绿灯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you've captured
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the notorious Acceleration T. Greenlight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:54.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,266)}通缉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.62,0:21:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在海底四处倒卖假驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been selling phony driver's licenses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,throughout the seabed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:56.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1512,590)}裤头村驾照\N懒惰鬼玛丽\N助步器老头\N鳗鱼卡洛斯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来也还能得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I would have gotten away with it, too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪这全海底最烂的司机把我害惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't for the worst driver in all the oceans
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道他那是想说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder who he meant by that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do go on
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  我跟加速下了山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, Acceleration and I went down the mountain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开过了浓雾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we drove through the fog
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撞上了坚冰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we crashed on the ice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱那故事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love that story, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再讲一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell it again
